Cyberpunk style: A glowing translucent digital entity in humanoid form emerges from layers of cascading code streams, its body composed of interconnected geometric nodes and pulsing data pathways. The figure stands at the center of a dark virtual space, surrounded by floating holographic panels displaying intricate circuit-like patterns in electric blue and neon orange. Streams of light flow from the entity's core outward like neural connections, linking to abstract floating interface elements. The atmosphere is moody with deep shadows pierced by sharp technological illumination. Small particle effects scatter throughout the scene like digital fireflies. The composition emphasizes the mysterious power of this digital being as a hidden force orchestrating complex systems behind the scenes.
